response.overview: SU closed out 2016 with its marquee event, Breaking Barriers 4. Mercedes Martinez had to prove herself to WSU Champion Allie when she faced the returning LuFisto. The dominate Taeler Hendrix faced off against an angry Jade. Meanwhile, the Fella Twins defended the WSU Tag Team Championships against the team of Annie Social and Missy Sampson, now known as the Backseat Girls. But in the Main Event, Leva Bates sought vengeance when she was challenged by Su Yung for the WSU Spirit Championship. All this and so much more went down at Breaking Barriers 4. You will be able to catch the Delayed iPPV Broadcast at CZWStudios.com. But for those who can't wait, please continue reading for the official result.
response.title: WSU Breaking Barriers IV
